{"tid":320526,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"【DSE放榜】學生倒米？校外驚現「勸世文」叫人唔好入樹仁","createTime":"2017-07-13T14:48:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-13T16:54:40.000Z","uid":69289,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"98f340ddf9735fffd6d6954df08496d31df3ebad","tid":320526,"uid":69289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T14:48:01.000Z","msg":"文憑試放榜，除通過聯招升上八大外，私立大學亦成為成績稍遜學生的另一出路。其中算是熱門選擇的樹仁大學早上校外出現多幅「倒米」直幡和大字報，稱入讀樹仁將令學生「悔終生」，呼籲考生入讀前要三思。<br />\n<br />\n記者 賴莉娜 張珮琪<br />\n<br />\n有人分別在樹仁校外的街燈、樓梯旁的山坡掛出寫上「入樹仁悔終生」、「OU恒管更稱心」的直幡，並貼出多張圖文並茂的「大字報」力數樹仁12宗罪，包括早前被《蘋果》踢爆多名懷疑學歷造假的導師至今仍有任教、學校設備如中學又殘舊、食堂食物質素差，甚至混雜膠片、牙線和玻璃等。<br />\n校方稱已派人移走有關直幡，因暫未知是甚麼人掛直幡和貼大字報，現未有任何跟進行動。<br />\n<br />\n下午超過50人到樹仁索取入學表格，應屆文憑試考生黃同學表示，心儀社會學和社會工作，次選會到城大的副學士，同是報讀社會學系，他對升學選擇少感無奈，「除左retake（重讀）之外都冇乜出路，入唔到大學就同5科合格係同一水平咁」。另一考生Angie希望入讀新聞系或社會工作系，她不滿香港的教學制度，「而家嘅教育制度都係標榜一定要入到大學先好」，希望社會理解讀大學不是唯一出路。  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20160713/large/1468392276_9a87.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20160713%2Flarge%2F1468392276_9a87.jpg&h=6d1c979c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人在樹仁大學校外掛上直幡，勸告考生不要入讀。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20160713/55352471\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20160713%2F55352471&d=bjv8BfnKRwgM3r48%2F2rr5JUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=0b9fac49\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20160713%2F55352471&h=2aa343a1\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20160713/55352471</a>"},{"pid":"a138c7b40f3da7af322398418d39d6771eba53de","tid":320526,"uid":69289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T14:52:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>疑收生不足　樹仁大學玩cold call招生</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n中學文憑試放榜約兩周，樹仁大學疑因收生不足，上周二(19日)向大約30間中學發出信件，內容指該校正進行16/17年度新生錄取階段，尚有少量學位供同學報讀，若該校學生文憑試4科主修加1科選修總成績達14分，將獲優先錄取，學生可於23日或之前，㩗文憑試成績單到該校報到。<br />\n<br />\n樹仁大學回覆東網時證實信中內容真確，但否認因為收生不足仍有學額而發信招生。該校表示去年亦有向中學發出有關信件，今年共向大約30間關係友好的中學發信，邀請校長推薦學生報讀任何學系，又指招生階段之前已聯絡有關學校校長可推薦學生。該校指並非必定錄取所有獲推薦學生，倘獲推薦的學生成績與以一般途徑報讀的學生相等，才會優先錄取。<br />\n<br />\n據樹仁大學網頁資料，其收生標準是申請人於文憑試考取中國語文科3級或以上；英國語文科 3級或以上；數學科2級或以上；通識教育科2級或以上；及另加一科選修科達2級或以上成績。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20160725/photo/bkn-20160725111952545-0725_00822_001_01b.jpg?20160725123208\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20160725%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20160725111952545-0725_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20160725123208&h=5a7fb662&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n樹仁大學向多間中學發信，指尚有少量學位供同學報讀。(互聯網/資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20160725/bkn-20160725111952545-0725_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20160725%2Fbkn-20160725111952545-0725_00822_001.html&d=bjv8BfnKRwgM3r48%2F2rr5JUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=41c68eb9\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20160725/bkn-20160725111952545-0725_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"3d8a1cbbf6dfac293bea3fa910c35fa03c24c490","tid":320526,"uid":69289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T14:53:42.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://s31.postimg.org/hya1jsrjf/1468369688_76a5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs31.postimg.org%2Fhya1jsrjf%2F1468369688_76a5.jpg&h=15198782&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"f2c23c9528b4364340affce1a99f87b4146bc74f","tid":320526,"uid":75877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T15:37:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11eb7aea323486dcb6c61f9f7c3bc3565c1526ba","tid":320526,"uid":36820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T15:43:10.000Z","msg":"D字表現出有血有淚既感覺"},{"pid":"292d55be3649fa683f3fe91de922e7a9e07d00c9","tid":320526,"uid":110297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T16:08:00.000Z","msg":"14分就入到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"19f3ec2bd14f0be61f088a63acd1205aaa2f35cf","tid":320526,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T16:29:11.000Z","msg":"樹仁求學生入讀<br />\n恆管就買like <br />\n自資院校<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1c77987e5f64a5a0e1f251bb9ade2d613ac57ca","tid":320526,"uid":69289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T16:32:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>14分就入到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n出埋信，你話呢?"},{"pid":"3a2e2f1880057b2c84c66d28649e8f293cf81c1f","tid":320526,"uid":69289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T16:32:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79cf5e89e583bd33292d491a9db58b45f00cd61d","tid":320526,"uid":122142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T16:40:46.000Z","msg":"聽d師兄講真係唔好入樹仁<br />\n一入此門<br />\n萬劫不復"},{"pid":"335d4289ae2fa738b9773adb3c2ef020c42654a6","tid":320526,"uid":6964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T16:54:40.000Z","msg":"會唔會執笠"}]}